Test this after example 10

Close the client.
Add the following lines to the usr/local/mysql/data/my.cnf file, in the [client] section:

# SSL 
ssl-cert=/etc/mysql-ssl/client-cert.pem 
ssl-key=/etc/mysql-ssl/client-key.pem

...and check that the client starts again.
After testing this example, erase these lines and restart the client.

